{"tid":1092456,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"沙拿被罰20下掌上壓？","createTime":"2019-04-05T00:09:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-05T04:38:42.000Z","uid":153600,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"86ccaf22142771d6bf3bfa47d5fab48bce6ab281","tid":1092456,"uid":153600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T00:09:22.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=Ibp2r5avkWIk14HZtW%2BzJx21egSez4RG9A7txFtatZY%3D&h=24b33bd2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】沙拿與隊友在操練中參與了「鬥射中眉」挑戰賽，可惜這名埃及翼鋒成為了最終輸家。<br />\n<br />\n近期在利物浦鬧入球荒的翼鋒穆罕默德沙拿（Mohamed Salah），在本周一次操練中與隊友洛夫雲、韋拿杜姆和阿歷士張伯倫一起參與了「鬥射中眉」挑戰賽，單看參賽名單，大家應對沙拿勝出十分有信心，但事情發展卻非預期一樣。<br />\n<br />\n4名球員中以洛夫雲的腳法最出眾，合共在試射及正式比賽中射中鬥眉3次，更大膽嘗試rabonna射門，以揶揄隊友。其後韋拿杜姆、張伯倫和沙拿進入「突然死亡」階段，前兩者分別成功射中門眉，而最後主射的沙拿此時竟將皮球送入網窩，令他成為了最終輸家，在其他3名隊友陪同下，被罰20下掌上壓。<br />\n<br />\n利物浦將於英國時間周五晚上作客修咸頓，紅軍方面當然希望沙拿在比賽中重拾射門鞋，順利全取3分，繼續壓逼爭冠對手曼城。<br />\n<br />\n相關片段：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=146&amp;v=1z6S1XPIX6w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Ftime_continue%3D146%26v%3D1z6S1XPIX6w&d=Ibp2r5avkWIk14HZtW%2BzJx21egSez4RG9A7txFtatZY%3D&h=c4ccf1ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=146&amp;v=1z6S1XPIX6w</a>"},{"pid":"4b234100210748a9e912e8664ac81b6a479c796e","tid":1092456,"uid":7119,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T00:37:02.000Z","msg":"平時踢又唔見沙拿射入網<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9641586b609f7e97c5da240ee2b3518a218836e0","tid":1092456,"uid":27485,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T00:40:57.000Z","msg":"張伯倫原來踢得番？<br />\n咁曼城仲咁比心機踢黎做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2df6f3ffeafcc25b7184fabc7665f30026ad20db","tid":1092456,"uid":209773,"like":